## Knighthoods

### Knight of Blood

#### Presence of Blood
*3rd-level Knight of Blood feature*

<div style='margin-top:-4px;'></div>

Whenever you deal damage, you regain a number of hit points equal to your proficiency bonus, up to the amount of damage dealt.

At 18th level, this benefit extends to all allies within 30 feet.

