### Knight of Frost
#### Presence of Frost
*3rd-level Knight of Frost feature*

<div style='margin-top:-4px;'></div>

Your body is filled with the chill of deep winter. You gain resistance to cold damage, can tolerate temperatures as low as -100 degrees Fahrenheit, and ignore difficult terrain created by ice and snow.

Additionally, whenever you deal damage with a weapon attack, the target takes an additional amount of cold damage equal to your proficiency bonus. 

